  "texts": [
    "Moreover, it could suggest ways in which the principles could be operationalized.",
    "Google DeepMind's Responsibility and Safety Council (RSC) is \"tasked with helping to uphold [their] AI principles\" [62].",
    "For example, the RSC might decide that releasing a model that can easily be misused would violate their principle \"be socially beneficial\" [64].But how much would interpreting ethics principles reduce risks?",
    "It would be more effective if the principles play a key role within the company.",
    "For example, Google's motto \"don't be evil\"-which it quietly removed in 2018-used to be part of its code of conduct and, reportedly, had a significant influence on its culture [47]."
  ],
